        <updateDate>2007-06-21T17:43:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Preventing the Endangerment of Children on Recreational Lands by Sexual Violators Act - Prohibits an individual convicted of a sexual offense involving a minor from serving in the Department of the Interior or the Department of Agriculture.</p><p>Provides that this Act does not require the separation of any employee or contractor whose service began before enactment of this Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
